  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TNT25">
<l>miṉṉilaṅku tiruvuruvum periya tōḷuṅ</l>
<l>karimuṉinta kaittalamuṅ kaṇṇum vāyum</l>
<l>taṉṉalarnta naṟuntuḻāy malariṉ kīḻē</l>
<l>tāḻntilaṅkum makaramcēr kuḻaiyuṅ kāṭṭi</l>
<l>eṉṉalaṉu meṉṉiṟaiyu meñcin taiyu</l>
<l>meṉvaḷaiyuṅ koṇṭeṉṉai yāḷuṅ koṇṭu</l>
<l>poṉṉalarnta naṟuñceruntip poḻili ṉūṭē</l>
<l>puṉalaraṅka mūreṉṟu pōyi ṉārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>[After] revealing [his] sacred form flashing like lightning, his broad shoulders,</l>
<l rend="indent">hands that raged at an elephant, his eyes and lips,</l>
<l>And earrings with makara that flash, hanging below</l>
<l rend="indent">[his chaplet of] fragrant, flowering tulasī,</l>
<l>Taking my virtue, my perfection, my thoughts,</l>
<l rend="indent">and my bangles, taking me as [his] slave,</l>
<l>He went saying, “[My] city is Araṅkam in the river</l>
<l rend="indent">midst groves of fragrant gold-blossomed campaka.”</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
